{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1072,"text":"I want to tell you a story about a girl."},{"time":4515,"text":"But I can't tell you her real name."},{"time":7015,"text":"So let's just call her Hadiza."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9561,"text":"Hadiza is 20."},{"time":11639,"text":"She's shy,"},{"time":12814,"text":"but she has a beautiful smile\nthat lights up her face."},{"time":16959,"text":"But she's in constant pain."},{"time":20643,"text":"And she will likely be on medication\nfor the rest of her life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25046,"text":"Do you want to know why?"},{"time":27964,"text":"Hadiza is a Chibok girl,"},{"time":30845,"text":"and on April 14, 2014, she was kidnapped"},{"time":34102,"text":"by Boko Haram terrorists."},{"time":36470,"text":"She managed to escape, though,"},{"time":39003,"text":"by jumping off the truck\nthat was carrying the girls."},{"time":42224,"text":"But when she landed,\nshe broke both her legs,"},{"time":45541,"text":"and she had to crawl on her tummy\nto hide in the bushes."},{"time":48985,"text":"She told me she was terrified\nthat Boko Haram would come back for her."},{"time":53704,"text":"She was one of 57 girls who would escape\nby jumping off trucks that day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58355,"text":"This story, quite rightly, caused ripples"},{"time":60920,"text":"around the world."},{"time":62316,"text":"People like Michelle Obama,\nMalala and others"},{"time":65610,"text":"lent their voices in protest,"},{"time":67726,"text":"and at about the same time --\nI was living in London at the time --"},{"time":71011,"text":"I was sent from London to Abuja\nto cover the World Economic Forum"},{"time":75678,"text":"that Nigeria was hosting\nfor the first time."},{"time":78655,"text":"But when we arrived, it was clear\nthat there was only one story in town."},{"time":83909,"text":"We put the government under pressure."},{"time":85778,"text":"We asked tough questions\nabout what they were doing"},{"time":88364,"text":"to bring these girls back."},{"time":90379,"text":"Understandably,"},{"time":92127,"text":"they weren't too happy\nwith our line of questioning,"},{"time":94958,"text":"and let's just say we received\nour fair share of \"alternative facts.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":98731,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":101436,"text":"Influential Nigerians\nwere telling us at the time"},{"time":104658,"text":"that we were na√Øve,"},{"time":106679,"text":"we didn't understand\nthe political situation in Nigeria."},{"time":110900,"text":"But they also told us"},{"time":113019,"text":"that the story of the Chibok girls"},{"time":115651,"text":"was a hoax."},{"time":118265,"text":"Sadly, this hoax narrative has persisted,"},{"time":120989,"text":"and there are still people\nin Nigeria today"},{"time":123303,"text":"who believe that the Chibok girls\nwere never kidnapped."},{"time":126931,"text":"Yet I was talking to people like these --"},{"time":130401,"text":"devastated parents,"},{"time":132130,"text":"who told us that on the day\nBoko Haram kidnapped their daughters,"},{"time":136208,"text":"they ran into the Sambisa Forest\nafter the trucks carrying their daughters."},{"time":140806,"text":"They were armed with machetes,\nbut they were forced to turn back"},{"time":144558,"text":"because Boko Haram had guns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147345,"text":"For two years, inevitably,\nthe news agenda moved on,"},{"time":151032,"text":"and for two years,"},{"time":152786,"text":"we didn't hear much\nabout the Chibok girls."},{"time":155969,"text":"Everyone presumed they were dead."},{"time":158233,"text":"But in April last year,"},{"time":160244,"text":"I was able to obtain this video."},{"time":163036,"text":"This is a still from the video"},{"time":164800,"text":"that Boko Haram filmed as a proof of life,"},{"time":168923,"text":"and through a source,\nI obtained this video."},{"time":172109,"text":"But before I could publish it,"},{"time":173670,"text":"I had to travel\nto the northeast of Nigeria"},{"time":176719,"text":"to talk to the parents, to verify it."},{"time":179317,"text":"I didn't have to wait\ntoo long for confirmation."},{"time":183630,"text":"One of the mothers,\nwhen she watched the video, told me"},{"time":186984,"text":"that if she could have reached\ninto the laptop"},{"time":189708,"text":"and pulled our her child from the laptop,"},{"time":193751,"text":"she would have done so."},{"time":196203,"text":"For those of you who are parents,\nlike myself, in the audience,"},{"time":199449,"text":"you can only imagine the anguish"},{"time":202301,"text":"that that mother felt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205601,"text":"This video would go on to kick-start\nnegotiation talks with Boko Haram."},{"time":212179,"text":"And a Nigerian senator told me\nthat because of this video"},{"time":216171,"text":"they entered into those talks,"},{"time":218188,"text":"because they had long presumed\nthat the Chibok girls were dead."},{"time":222639,"text":"Twenty-one girls were freed\nin October last year."},{"time":227365,"text":"Sadly, nearly 200 of them\nstill remain missing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231691,"text":"I must confess that I have not been\na dispassionate observer"},{"time":235912,"text":"covering this story."},{"time":237122,"text":"I am furious when I think\nabout the wasted opportunities"},{"time":242232,"text":"to rescue these girls."},{"time":243445,"text":"I am furious when I think about\nwhat the parents have told me,"},{"time":247369,"text":"that if these were daughters\nof the rich and the powerful,"},{"time":250167,"text":"they would have been found much earlier."},{"time":254281,"text":"And I am furious"},{"time":256313,"text":"that the hoax narrative,"},{"time":258265,"text":"I firmly believe,"},{"time":260167,"text":"caused a delay;"},{"time":262303,"text":"it was part of the reason\nfor the delay in their return."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266680,"text":"This illustrates to me\nthe deadly danger of fake news."},{"time":271219,"text":"So what can we do about it?"},{"time":273883,"text":"There are some very smart people,"},{"time":275824,"text":"smart engineers at Google and Facebook,"},{"time":278307,"text":"who are trying to use technology\nto stop the spread of fake news."},{"time":283396,"text":"But beyond that, I think\neverybody here -- you and I --"},{"time":288171,"text":"we have a role to play in that."},{"time":290382,"text":"We are the ones who share the content."},{"time":292699,"text":"We are the ones who share\nthe stories online."},{"time":295234,"text":"In this day and age, we're all publishers,"},{"time":298535,"text":"and we have responsibility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301050,"text":"In my job as a journalist,"},{"time":303384,"text":"I check, I verify."},{"time":305436,"text":"I trust my gut, but I ask tough questions."},{"time":309620,"text":"Why is this person telling me this story?"},{"time":312520,"text":"What do they have to gain\nby sharing this information?"},{"time":316043,"text":"Do they have a hidden agenda?"},{"time":318682,"text":"I really believe that we must all start\nto ask tougher questions"},{"time":324197,"text":"of information that we discover online."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329673,"text":"Research shows that some of us\ndon't even read beyond headlines"},{"time":335428,"text":"before we share stories."},{"time":337555,"text":"Who here has done that?"},{"time":339944,"text":"I know I have."},{"time":342435,"text":"But what if"},{"time":345295,"text":"we stopped taking information\nthat we discover at face value?"},{"time":350250,"text":"What if we stop to think\nabout the consequence"},{"time":353847,"text":"of the information that we pass on"},{"time":356320,"text":"and its potential to incite\nviolence or hatred?"},{"time":360595,"text":"What if we stop to think\nabout the real-life consequences"},{"time":365154,"text":"of the information that we share?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368105,"text":"Thank you very much for listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369929,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}